find_library(sdl2_core_library
  names sdl2
  hints
  $env{sdl2dir}
  path_suffixes lib64 lib
  paths
  /sw
  /opt/local
  /opt/csw
  /opt
)

      names sdl2main
      hints
      $env{sdl2dir}
      path_suffixes lib64 lib
      paths

      /opt
    )

        env sdlsounddir
        env sdldir
)

                names ${_python_library_names}
                path_suffixes
                "python${_python_short_version}/config"
                "python${_python_major_version}${_python_minor_version}/config"
                paths
                ${_python_library_dir}
                ${_python_prefix}/lib
                ${_python_prefix}/libs
                ${_python_library_dir}/x86_64-linux-gnu/
                no_default_path)

                  names python${_python_major_version}${_python_minor_version}_d python

                  [hkey_local_machine\\software\\python\\pythoncore\\${_current_version}\\installpath]/libs
                  [hkey_current_user\\software\\python\\pythoncore\\${_current_version}\\installpath]/libs
                  )
